This online course is based on a California Stormwater Quality Association (CASQA) Best Management Practice handbook and is designed to provide continuing education for professional engineers, municipal and regulatory agency employees, developers, construction companies, and others to increase their knowledge of stormwater best management practices.
Students complete our course using a CASQA BMP handbook and a study guide on CD. The final exam is completed online, allowing for instant grade results.
